了解，你現在的「純新光」定義又多了一個條件：

純新光條件

1. CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)
2. 計算風險時只看 FLG=2、3 的 SK
3. CustomerNo 不存在於 VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT

也就是：

NOT EXISTS
(
    SELECT 1
    FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
    WHERE v.CustomerNo = s.TS_CUST_ID
)

⸻

完整版可以這樣寫：

WITH PURE_SK AS
(
    SELECT DISTINCT
           s.TS_CUST_ID
    FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
    WHERE s.CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)
      AND NOT EXISTS
      (
          SELECT 1
          FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
          WHERE v.CustomerNo = s.TS_CUST_ID
      )
),
SRC AS
(
    SELECT
        s.TS_CUST_ID,
        MAX(
            CASE n.HIGHRISK
                WHEN 'H' THEN 3
                WHEN 'M' THEN 2
                WHEN 'L' THEN 1
                ELSE 0
            END
        ) AS SRC_RISK_NUM
    FROM PURE_SK p
    JOIN BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
      ON p.TS_CUST_ID = s.TS_CUST_ID
     AND s.CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)
    JOIN Customer_Migrate_buffer c
      ON s.SK_CUST_ID = c.CustomerNo
    JOIN Cust_NP_Migrate_buffer n
      ON c.CIF_KEY = n.CIF_KEY
    GROUP BY s.TS_CUST_ID
),
TGT AS
(
    SELECT
        CustomerNo,
        CASE HIGHRISK
            WHEN 'H' THEN 3
            WHEN 'M' THEN 2
            WHEN 'L' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END AS TGT_RISK_NUM
    FROM BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT
)
SELECT
    s.TS_CUST_ID,
    CASE s.SRC_RISK_NUM
        WHEN 3 THEN 'H'
        WHEN 2 THEN 'M'
        WHEN 1 THEN 'L'
    END AS SOURCE_RISK,
    CASE t.TGT_RISK_NUM
        WHEN 3 THEN 'H'
        WHEN 2 THEN 'M'
        WHEN 1 THEN 'L'
    END AS TARGET_RISK
FROM SRC s
JOIN TGT t
    ON s.TS_CUST_ID = t.CustomerNo
WHERE s.SRC_RISK_NUM <> t.TGT_RISK_NUM
ORDER BY s.TS_CUST_ID;

⸻

如果你只是想先確認「純新光名單有多少人」，可以先跑：

SELECT DISTINCT
       s.TS_CUST_ID
FROM BANCS_SK_CUST_INFO s
WHERE s.CUST_RE_NO_FLG IN (2,3)
  AND NOT EXISTS
  (
      SELECT 1
      FROM VERIFY..BSA_SUB_CUST_FACT v
      WHERE v.CustomerNo = s.TS_CUST_ID
  );

這樣就能看到實際進入驗證的純新光客戶數。